data.description: Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! This house, nestled in a peaceful subdivision just minutes from downtown Madisonville, won't stay on the market for long.Step inside this split foyer home and discover an expansive open floor plan boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a bonus room, and a spacious 2-car garage.Upon entering the upstairs level, you'll be greeted by beautiful, continuous LVP flooring that seamlessly flows through the living room and kitchen.The newly upgraded, stunning large tile floors in the bathrooms will make you wonder how you ever lived without them!The Owners' Suite offers ample space for your comfort and relaxation.Head downstairs to find 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, a bonus room, and the laundry room.The downstairs bedroom boasts a massive walk-in closet, perfect for those with an extensive wardrobe collection.Additional storage space is conveniently available both downstairs and in the attic.Step outside to the generously sized, fully fenced backyard, providing the perfect space for entertaining friends and family or allowing your children to play safely.This home also features a back deck and storage shed.Rest assured, the owners have meticulously maintained this house!Don't wait - call today to schedule your showing and seize this exceptional opportunity!
